data.description: FALL in love with this adorable family home with an open floorplan and split bedroom arrangement * Newly renovated kitchen with granite counter tops, flooring, appliances, fixtures, and more. Other features that your family will LOVE include fresh paint inside and out * luxury wood flooring * ceramic tile * new light fixtures throughout * wrap around breakfast bar * eat in kitchen area * large family area * corner WBFP fireplace * guest bedrooms, split by a large guest bath * private en suite with renovated bath, lrg walk in shower with rain head and infinite glass surround * enclosed sunroom that  could be used as another bedroom, game room, or office space * walk out covered patio * large fenced backyard * and storage building, And just a few additional fun facts...Water heater replaced in 2020, HVAC in 2022, extra blown insulation and roof in 2021. Such a PERFECT HOME for your family to enjoy and to make memories for years to come!
